05:10.277 --> 05:12.712
Well, I have no idea
who those people are,

05:12.779 --> 05:14.747
but I'm on board.
Let's hear it.
Okay.

05:14.815 --> 05:17.550
It's just... It's a little
rough, but, uh...

05:17.618 --> 05:19.752
