in the tent.

33:11.314 --> 33:12.781
Okay. What do you want
from me here, Dad? I...

33:12.849 --> 33:15.717
I want you to apologize
for being inappropriate

33:15.785 --> 33:18.387
and promise me
you'll never do it again.

33:19.556 --> 33:23.058
Fine. I'm sorry.

33:23.126 --> 33:25.994
I won't have sleepovers with
anyone that might be gay

33:26.062 --> 33:27.996
