33:28.064 --> 33:30.732
Thank you.

33:35.972 --> 33:39.241
But maybe you could step
outside your comfort zone

33:39.309 --> 33:41.543
and educate yourself, so
if I have any questions,

33:41.611 --> 33:44.646
I could go to my dad, like
any straight son could.

33:50.323 --> 33:52.424
. Quiet,
please, children.

33:52.492 --> 33:54.960
I would like
to wish you and yours

33:55.028 --> 33:58.030
