in some kind of riot.

34:22.621 --> 34:23.889
Never fear, teammates.

34:23.956 --> 34:25.690
Now, it's a Broadway tradition
for nervous performers

34:25.759 --> 34:27.192
to take a shot of whiskey
before going on

34:27.260 --> 34:28.393
to calm their nerves

34:28.460 --> 34:29.995
and to mask the stench
of bad dental hygiene.

34:30.063 --> 34:32.331
