cough syrup.

34:41.741 --> 34:42.775
There's also cough syrup.

34:42.842 --> 34:43.742
ALL: Cheers.
To Ke$ha.

34:43.810 --> 34:44.842
Cheers. Ke$ha.

34:44.911 --> 34:46.210
To Ke$ha.
To Ke$ha.

34:46.279 --> 34:47.713
Thank you, Chief.

34:47.781 --> 34:49.915
And now,
performing the hit single,

34:49.983 --> 34:51.884
"Tik and also Tok"

34:51.951 --> 34:54.786
by rapper Ke-dollar-sign-ha,

34:54.853 --> 34:57.456
the New Directions.

34:57.524 --> 34:58.991
(microphone feedback squeals)

34:59.058 --> 35:00.759
